# game/S004.rpy:8
translate Chinese s004_333f72e4:

    voice "JYOSIA0002.ogg"
    girl_a "「有听说过莉莉·白金的会议的话题吗」"

# game/S004.rpy:11
translate Chinese s004_c0851598:

    voice "JYOSIB0002.ogg"
    girl_b "「当然有听过啦。从以前开始我就很在意的了」"

# game/S004.rpy:14
translate Chinese s004_b6286858:

    voice "JYOSIB0003.ogg"
    girl_b "「是今天放学后吧，之前因为功课繁重而无法出席，不过这次打算参与」"

# game/S004.rpy:19
translate Chinese s004_c61b599c:

    voice "SIZUKU0196.ogg"
    shizuku "「……莉莉·白金……？？」"

# game/S004.rpy:22
translate Chinese s004_3aa76da6:

    "这是第几次我听到这不熟识的词语了。"

# game/S004.rpy:23
translate Chinese s004_beb220de:

    "不只是一次两次，而是听过无数次。"

# game/S004.rpy:24
translate Chinese s004_d6b1c6b6:

    "而且不只是今天，在这一星期里已经听过数百次了。"

# game/S004.rpy:26
translate Chinese s004_9eed48b7:

    voice "SIZUKU0197.ogg"
    shizuku "「还是不太了解洋文……从语感看来，应该是西洋甜食店，或是西洋服装店之类的……唔～嗯……」"

# game/S004.rpy:29
translate Chinese s004_35a46148:

    voice "JYOSIA0003.ogg"
    girl_a "「那个……雫大人，从刚刚开始是不是一直在看着这边？」"

# game/S004.rpy:32
translate Chinese s004_da53c4ba:

    voice "SIZUKU0198.ogg"
    shizuku "「诶？那，那是……呃……」"

# game/S004.rpy:35
translate Chinese s004_335a9cfe:

    voice "JYOSIA0004.ogg"
    girl_a "「难道雫大人也对『莉莉·白金』有兴趣？」"

# game/S004.rpy:38
translate Chinese s004_7773f637:

    voice "SIZUKU0199.ogg"
    shizuku "「……要说有兴趣，倒不如说很在意……」"

# game/S004.rpy:41
translate Chinese s004_e148fc81:

    voice "JYOSIB0004.ogg"
    girl_b "「等等，你在对雫御前说什么话？我们就暂且不说，雫御前是没可能对这有兴趣的吧？」"

# game/S004.rpy:44
translate Chinese s004_b970214b:

    voice "JYOSIA0005.ogg"
    girl_a "「也，也对呢……真是非常抱歉，雫大人」"

# game/S004.rpy:47
translate Chinese s004_5fcc11da:

    voice "SIZUKU0200.ogg"
    shizuku "「不，不……没关系的……」"

# game/S004.rpy:50
translate Chinese s004_59bd66da:

    "然后跟我对话的女孩就继续说着『莉莉·白金』的话题。"

# game/S004.rpy:51
translate Chinese s004_44db9452:

    "明明不在意比较好，但刚刚的对话依然在我耳边回荡着。"

# game/S004.rpy:53
translate Chinese s004_78c0b0d7:

    voice "SIZUKU0201.ogg"
    shizuku "「啊啊……可能问问刚才那个女孩比较好吧……」"

# game/S004.rpy:59
translate Chinese s004_dbe4802d:

    "……然后，在数天后。"

# game/S004.rpy:65
translate Chinese s004_c8d8b2bb:

    voice "JYOSIC0000.ogg"
    girl_c "「有没有听说？『莉莉·白金』的会员超过五十人了喔」"

# game/S004.rpy:68
translate Chinese s004_af8a2665:

    voice "JYOSID0000.ogg"
    girl_d "「当然知道啦。我也是其中的一员呢。是会员ＮＯ.１５喔{note}」"

# game/S004.rpy:71
translate Chinese s004_30913f02:

    voice "JYOSIC0001.ogg"
    girl_c "「嘛，原来这么早就入会了呢」"

# game/S004.rpy:74
translate Chinese s004_548e7e52:

    voice "JYOSIE0000.ogg"
    girl_e "「呼呼，太天真了。我其实，是会员ＮＯ.１喔」"

# game/S004.rpy:79
translate Chinese s004_5857e54b:

    voice "SIZUKU0202.ogg"
    shizuku "「……无论哪里都……唉～」"

# game/S004.rpy:82
translate Chinese s004_daa01805:

    "不知从何时开始，『莉莉·白金』这个单词在整个学年中流传开来了。"

# game/S004.rpy:83
translate Chinese s004_afc344f8:

    "而且是在日常会话中，像是理所当然般的使用着。"

# game/S004.rpy:84
translate Chinese s004_67cca47f:

    "一听到这话题，就突然觉得有点疏离感。"

# game/S004.rpy:88
translate Chinese s004_b094d7dd:

    voice "SIZUKU0203.ogg"
    shizuku "「总觉得……有点后悔」"

# game/S004.rpy:91
translate Chinese s004_780db8df:

    "现在，只要问一下那边的三个人的话，一定会说给我听的。"

# game/S004.rpy:92
translate Chinese s004_23c813b8:

    "但是，有点害怕她们三人态度的变化，就算想去问也没法问。"

# game/S004.rpy:93
translate Chinese s004_5167e5a0:

    "『雫大人竟然，不知道莉莉·白金是什么……』"

# game/S004.rpy:94
translate Chinese s004_0ddc62ff:

    "『已经快变成这个校园的常识了喔，常识』"

# game/S004.rpy:95
translate Chinese s004_b0f32bdf:

    "『果然雫御前已经跟世界脱节了呢……』"

# game/S004.rpy:99
translate Chinese s004_ab9d0b78:

    voice "SIZUKU0204.ogg"
    shizuku "「……绝对不想听到，那样的话……」"

# game/S004.rpy:102
translate Chinese s004_afb4c0ad:

    "明明以前人们常常以我为中心的。"

# game/S004.rpy:103
translate Chinese s004_b7f360c8:

    "在这种时候却连一个值得信赖的朋友都没有。"

# game/S004.rpy:104
translate Chinese s004_02890620:

    "明明朋友可以算是一生的宝物，但看来我是没有的。"

# game/S004.rpy:106
translate Chinese s004_27863970:

    voice "SIZUKU0205.ogg"
    shizuku "「总觉得有点像缺乏情报，与时代脱节的旧人类啊……啊」"

# game/S004.rpy:109
translate Chinese s004_2fac8ceb:

    "对喔。"

# game/S004.rpy:113
translate Chinese s004_1197abb6:

    voice "SIZUKU0206.ogg"
    shizuku "「即使没有朋友，也是有恋人的呢……嗯{note}」"

# game/S004.rpy:123
translate Chinese s004_61bdae47:

    voice "ERISU_0161.ogg"
    eris "「不知道呢」"

# game/S004.rpy:129
translate Chinese s004_a068b245:

    voice "SIZUKU0207.ogg"
    shizuku "「诶诶，连爱丽丝也不知道啊……啊啊，太可惜了」"

# game/S004.rpy:132
translate Chinese s004_cbf8f1db:

    "本以为与我不同，经常跟同学聊天的爱丽丝会知道。"

# game/S004.rpy:133
translate Chinese s004_47d543a9:

    "竟然这么直接回答我『不知道』。"

# game/S004.rpy:135
translate Chinese s004_7418a768:

    voice "SIZUKU0208.ogg"
    shizuku "「啊——啊……这样就失去唯一的情报源了」"

# game/S004.rpy:141
translate Chinese s004_0a54bb73:

    voice "ERISU_0162.ogg"
    eris "「这种事，只要问一下旁边的人就行……」"

# game/S004.rpy:147
translate Chinese s004_ad62d039:

    voice "SIZUKU0209.ogg"
    shizuku "「如果能简单地做到的话，就不用这样辛苦了！」"

# game/S004.rpy:150
translate Chinese s004_73d1c2b2:

    voice "ERISU_0163.ogg"
    eris "「哼……是雫的性格问题呢。就不会坦率地说『请告诉我』」"

# game/S004.rpy:156
translate Chinese s004_60c7f560:

    voice "SIZUKU0210.ogg"
    shizuku "「……正是如此」"

# game/S004.rpy:159
translate Chinese s004_a02e8681:

    "真讨厌自己这样奇怪的性格。"

# game/S004.rpy:161
translate Chinese s004_9035226f:

    voice "ERISU_0164.ogg"
    eris "「那不如由我向大家打听一下？」"

# game/S004.rpy:164
translate Chinese s004_24cccab4:

    voice "SIZUKU0211.ogg"
    shizuku "「……的确，作为年级之友的爱丽丝，比较容易收集情报……但那也不行」"

# game/S004.rpy:170
translate Chinese s004_23a747dc:

    voice "ERISU_0165.ogg"
    eris "「诶诶～，为什么？」"

# game/S004.rpy:176
translate Chinese s004_60bcdf74:

    voice "SIZUKU0212.ogg"
    shizuku "「因为我跟爱丽丝就像一心同体，即使是由爱丽丝去打听，那都算是我输了」"

# game/S004.rpy:179
translate Chinese s004_8f314d63:

    "而且还要让爱丽丝代替我去问。"

# game/S004.rpy:180
translate Chinese s004_22b381b4:

    "这不就像什么都做不到的孩子吗。"

# game/S004.rpy:181
translate Chinese s004_98f487ff:

    "说到恋人，就应该是对等的关系。"

# game/S004.rpy:182
translate Chinese s004_6eaebc13:

    "不能在这里撒娇的。"

# game/S004.rpy:187
translate Chinese s004_32bc28a2:

    voice "ERISU_0166.ogg"
    eris "「虽然不太理解是什么理论……总之就是我和雫两人是一体的吧？呀{heart}」"

# game/S004.rpy:193
translate Chinese s004_988c67b5:

    voice "SIZUKU0213.ogg"
    shizuku "「等等爱丽丝，这里是课室喔，不能干出太引人注意的事……啊啊，不行」"

# game/S004.rpy:199
translate Chinese s004_72bc8186:

    "……总之先推开抱过来的爱丽丝，我再次思考起来。"

# game/S004.rpy:207
translate Chinese s004_60e63188:

    voice "SIZUKU0214.ogg"
    shizuku "「『Ｐｌａｔｉｎｕｍ』应该是指，白金吧」"

# game/S004.rpy:213
translate Chinese s004_785dc5dd:

    voice "ERISU_0167.ogg"
    eris "「应该是喔，也没有别的了吧」"

# game/S004.rpy:216
translate Chinese s004_7cce1608:

    "直译的话应该就是那样了，所以就那样理解好了。那样的话……"

# game/S004.rpy:218
translate Chinese s004_4c2a9fb9:

    voice "SIZUKU0215.ogg"
    shizuku "「……是莉莉，吧。这是最重要的」"

# game/S004.rpy:224
translate Chinese s004_2d15506e:

    voice "ERISU_0168.ogg"
    eris "「太简单了，让人难以理解呢。应该是……人的名字？」"

# game/S004.rpy:227
translate Chinese s004_c7aa92c2:

    voice "SIZUKU0216.ogg"
    shizuku "「那就是，白金的莉莉……总觉得那只是，一个绰号而已」"

# game/S004.rpy:233
translate Chinese s004_a405d5e9:

    voice "ERISU_0169.ogg"
    eris "「还可能是个代号」"

# game/S004.rpy:239
translate Chinese s004_71a83111:

    voice "SIZUKU0217.ogg"
    shizuku "「代，代号？」"

# game/S004.rpy:242
translate Chinese s004_37e68e51:

    "爱丽丝的眼睛发出了异光。"

# game/S004.rpy:243
translate Chinese s004_7f7e4e3a:

    "那应该是，确信了一些事。"

# game/S004.rpy:245
translate Chinese s004_8cfc48d0:

    voice "ERISU_0170.ogg"
    eris "「在米卡女暗中活跃的女间谍的别称，不知不觉中这学院渐渐被『莉莉·白金』支配了」"

# game/S004.rpy:248
translate Chinese s004_e3cd4e8c:

    voice "SIZUKU0218.ogg"
    shizuku "「太恐怖了……竟然有那么惊人的事实……」"

# game/S004.rpy:254
translate Chinese s004_659eb4e5:

    voice "ERISU_0171.ogg"
    eris "「……假的喔？」"

# game/S004.rpy:260
translate Chinese s004_07056853:

    voice "SIZUKU0219.ogg"
    shizuku "「诶？？」"

# game/S004.rpy:266
translate Chinese s004_a8b251ba:

    voice "ERISU_0172.ogg"
    eris "「说笑啦，雫就不要太认真啦」"

# game/S004.rpy:272
translate Chinese s004_66195d1c:

    voice "SIZUKU0220.ogg"
    shizuku "「才，才没有认真，才不可能会认真吧」"

# game/S004.rpy:275
translate Chinese s004_bbd5c1f0:

    "只有一点，真的只有一点，稍微心惊肉跳了。"

# game/S004.rpy:280
translate Chinese s004_e8c5bb0e:

    voice "SIZUKU0221.ogg"
    shizuku "「人家在认真地讨论……就给我认真点啊，爱丽丝！」"

# game/S004.rpy:286
translate Chinese s004_9d332fe2:

    voice "ERISU_0173.ogg"
    eris "「啊嗯……抱歉呢，我会认真地想的」"

# game/S004.rpy:289
translate Chinese s004_6f230cbf:

    "挽着手，爱丽丝也一起思考着。"

# game/S004.rpy:290
translate Chinese s004_884c800f:

    "我也让脑袋运转一下，果然到那里就想不下去了。"

# game/S004.rpy:295
translate Chinese s004_7605c89a:

    voice "ERISU_0174.ogg"
    eris "「……雫，那样的话倒不如」"

# game/S004.rpy:298
translate Chinese s004_3af2510f:

    "爱丽丝的手不经意地向我伸来。"

# game/S004.rpy:303
translate Chinese s004_d3ba9eef:

    voice "SIZUKU0222.ogg"
    shizuku "「等等！爱丽丝，你要干什么？」"

# game/S004.rpy:309
translate Chinese s004_5315a091:

    voice "ERISU_0175.ogg"
    eris "「为了转换气氛，我们来亲热亲热吧，雫{heart}」"

# game/S004.rpy:315
translate Chinese s004_3bcc9e8b:

    voice "SIZUKU0223.ogg"
    shizuku "「真是的，不行！才刚开始想吧」"

# game/S004.rpy:321
translate Chinese s004_d510ba68:

    voice "ERISU_0176.ogg"
    eris "「因为……难得能和雫一起，但要思考什么的太无聊了」"

# game/S004.rpy:324
translate Chinese s004_ab9076f9:

    "明明刚刚还在抒发己见，爱丽丝又抱过来了。"

# game/S004.rpy:329
translate Chinese s004_831b4643:

    voice "SIZUKU0224.ogg"
    shizuku "「不行，不行喔，这里是课室」"

# game/S004.rpy:335
translate Chinese s004_70f380fc:

    voice "ERISU_0177.ogg"
    eris "「没问题喔，谁也没有在看」"

# game/S004.rpy:338
translate Chinese s004_047ea110:

    voice "SIZUKU0225.ogg"
    shizuku "「才不是，大家都好好地在看着」"

# game/S004.rpy:344
translate Chinese s004_f90adfc0:

    voice "ERISU_0178.ogg"
    eris "「没有看啦……对吧？」"

# game/S004.rpy:347
translate Chinese s004_d1da50d1:

    "爱丽丝这样说道，在我们旁边聊着天的同学也一起将目光移开。"

# game/S004.rpy:348
translate Chinese s004_214fd291:

    "像是笼罩着『才没有妨碍到两人喔』的举动。"

# game/S004.rpy:353
translate Chinese s004_77d12a3c:

    voice "ERISU_0179.ogg"
    eris "「看吧，没有人看着这边喔……来，就堕入头昏眼花的世界吧{heart}」"

# game/S004.rpy:356
translate Chinese s004_733e836b:

    voice "SIZUKU0226.ogg"
    shizuku "「爱丽丝……真是的」"

# game/S004.rpy:359
translate Chinese s004_51fb574d:

    "她是这课室的支配者吗。"

# game/S004.rpy:360
translate Chinese s004_14075494:

    "就这样，结果没有什么进展，只是时间慢慢过去了而已。"

# game/S004.rpy:361
translate Chinese s004_9be72fd8:

    "仍然谜团重重……"

# game/S004.rpy:366
translate Chinese s004_793b3241:

    "在转移课室的途中，两个同学又在讨论有关『莉莉·白金』的话题。"

# game/S004.rpy:370
translate Chinese s004_181e3e60:

    voice "SIZUKU0227.ogg"
    shizuku "「才不想干偷听这种不体面的事……」"

# game/S004.rpy:373
translate Chinese s004_7f09d411:

    "可是想要理解事情的全部，要付出代价也是没办法的事。"

# game/S004.rpy:374
translate Chinese s004_95caebac:

    "就这样自言自语道，我边心里挣扎着，边若无其事地接近着两人。"

# game/S004.rpy:376
translate Chinese s004_87fc6cff:

    voice "JYOSIA0006.ogg"
    girl_a "「『莉莉·白金』的活动也大部分启动了呢，每天都变得充实了」"

# game/S004.rpy:379
translate Chinese s004_fb35aefe:

    voice "JYOSIB0005.ogg"
    girl_b "「现在我也很享受和会员的大家一起聊天」"

# game/S004.rpy:384
translate Chinese s004_c4fb9c62:

    voice "SIZUKU0228.ogg"
    shizuku "「能听到『会员』之类的话呢……」"

# game/S004.rpy:387
translate Chinese s004_94ee2d73:

    "果然，应该是些什么小组吧。"

# game/S004.rpy:388
translate Chinese s004_eef68645:

    "说来也听说会员人数超过了五十人。"

# game/S004.rpy:390
translate Chinese s004_c4ab6ea8:

    voice "JYOSIA0007.ogg"
    girl_a "「她也是一如以往，非常的美丽呢……」"

# game/S004.rpy:393
translate Chinese s004_1303b336:

    voice "JYOSIB0006.ogg"
    girl_b "「确实呢，让人不禁叹息」"

# game/S004.rpy:398
translate Chinese s004_cbab9100:

    voice "SIZUKU0229.ogg"
    shizuku "「……她……？」"

# game/S004.rpy:401
translate Chinese s004_15139179:

    "这样听起来，好像是在瞄准某一人呢。"

# game/S004.rpy:402
translate Chinese s004_9c5a86f2:

    "啊啊，我的思路越来越混乱了。"

# game/S004.rpy:403
translate Chinese s004_2d9f4659:

    "『莉莉·白金』是一个人呢，还是几个人呢。"

# game/S004.rpy:405
translate Chinese s004_59172377:

    voice "SIZUKU0230.ogg"
    shizuku "「呜……呜呜呜……不行啊，如果一直都对对方的反应存有恐惧，就一直不能到达真相的彼岸了！」"

# game/S004.rpy:408
translate Chinese s004_acd7074f:

    "这并不像平常追求着完美的我。"

# game/S004.rpy:412
translate Chinese s004_9c2d338e:

    voice "SIZUKU0231.ogg"
    shizuku "「这样的话……只能直接问了吧……」"

# game/S004.rpy:415
translate Chinese s004_57cb4842:

    "我不再想太多，从后面向两人问道。"

# game/S004.rpy:419
translate Chinese s004_5d7c9e0c:

    voice "SIZUKU0232.ogg"
    shizuku "「请，请问……」"

# game/S004.rpy:422
translate Chinese s004_2211eb96:

    voice "JYOSIA0008.ogg"
    girl_a "「啊，看看那边！」"

# game/S004.rpy:425
translate Chinese s004_2bddab80:

    voice "JYOSIB0007.ogg"
    girl_b "「在那边的是！」"

# game/S004.rpy:428
translate Chinese s004_dd22203e:

    "我的声音被两人欢喜的声音覆盖了。"

# game/S004.rpy:429
translate Chinese s004_7c0c9617:

    "途中，我的勇气越来越少了。"

# game/S004.rpy:433
translate Chinese s004_25e17203:

    voice "SIZUKU0233.ogg"
    shizuku "「啊啊，已经不行了……」"

# game/S004.rpy:436
translate Chinese s004_3f7d3180:

    "是不是应该放弃这件事呢。"

# game/S004.rpy:437
translate Chinese s004_63aa2c64:

    "相比起越来越消沉的我，面前的两人像是心跃起来的样子。"

# game/S004.rpy:438
translate Chinese s004_609dd1b2:

    "究竟，发生什么事了。"

# game/S004.rpy:439
translate Chinese s004_c3a3fae2:

    "顺着两人的视线，我看见了熟悉的背影。"

# game/S004.rpy:443
translate Chinese s004_fb17da20:

    voice "SIZUKU0234.ogg"
    shizuku "「那是，爱丽丝……」"

# game/S004.rpy:446
translate Chinese s004_8b2e06a3:

    "在爱丽丝注意到这边之前，她们便叫道。"

# game/S004.rpy:448
translate Chinese s004_de200813:

    voice "JYOSIA0009.ogg"
    girl_a "「莉莉大人」"

# game/S004.rpy:451
translate Chinese s004_c5e88596:

    voice "JYOSIB0008.ogg"
    girl_b "「贵安，莉莉大人」"

# game/S004.rpy:454
translate Chinese s004_b8d8cf1f:

    voice "SIZUKU0235.ogg"
    shizuku "「莉莉大人？」"

# game/S004.rpy:457
translate Chinese s004_03f88537:

    "两人果断地称呼爱丽丝为『莉莉大人』。"

# game/S004.rpy:459
translate Chinese s004_21f14be2:

    voice "SIZUKU0236.ogg"
    shizuku "「这究竟，是怎么一回事……？」"

# game/S004.rpy:466
translate Chinese s004_429fc802:

    "……之后。"

# game/S004.rpy:467
translate Chinese s004_d2038a87:

    "感到困惑的我询问着刚刚称呼爱丽丝为莉莉大人的两人。"

# game/S004.rpy:468
translate Chinese s004_a75e12ae:

    "变成这种情况，自己的羞耻感都不在意了。"

# game/S004.rpy:469
translate Chinese s004_6b40b7df:

    "这是和我最喜欢的爱丽丝有关系的。"

# game/S004.rpy:470
translate Chinese s004_f4b596b2:

    "所以，才不会拘谨这种小事。"

# game/S004.rpy:471
translate Chinese s004_0fd4d656:

    "………………"

# game/S004.rpy:472
translate Chinese s004_931e4e96:

    "然后终于知道『莉莉·白金』是怎么一回事。"

# game/S004.rpy:473
translate Chinese s004_12fca138:

    "根据她们所说，『莉莉·白金』是……"

# game/S004.rpy:474
translate Chinese s004_7a908b1f:

    "竟然是爱丽丝，和爱丽丝Ｆａｎｓｃｌｕｂ的名称。"

# game/S004.rpy:476
translate Chinese s004_dac6c243:

    voice "JYOSIA0010.ogg"
    girl_a "「啊，但是要跟爱丽丝大人搭话时，大家也经常会叫『莉莉大人』喔{note}」"

# game/S004.rpy:481
translate Chinese s004_591858ed:

    voice "SIZUKU0237.ogg"
    shizuku "「原来是……这样啊……」"

# game/S004.rpy:484
translate Chinese s004_36a8b3ba:

    "答案竟然这么近在眼前，连这都察觉不到的自己也太粗心大意了。"

# game/S004.rpy:485
translate Chinese s004_237d21b3:

    "爱丽丝也是。"

# game/S004.rpy:494
translate Chinese s004_fa8c9521:

    voice "SIZUKU0238.ogg"
    shizuku "「……好像是这么一回事喔」"

# game/S004.rpy:500
translate Chinese s004_c31db00f:

    voice "ERISU_0180.ogg"
    eris "「……说来大家也会像那样称呼我呢」"

# game/S004.rpy:503
translate Chinese s004_56fc2128:

    voice "SIZUKU0239.ogg"
    shizuku "「………………」"

# game/S004.rpy:509
translate Chinese s004_8977b699:

    voice "ERISU_0181.ogg"
    eris "「以前也是《银光·新星》……之类的吧？之前也被冠上这样的昵称，所以也搞不太懂」"

# game/S004.rpy:512
translate Chinese s004_9c1362b5:

    voice "ERISU_0182.ogg"
    eris "「以为都是类似的称号，所以没有太注意……嗯，雫，怎么了？」"

# game/S004.rpy:518
translate Chinese s004_538976c3:

    voice "SIZUKU0240.ogg"
    shizuku "「咕……真是的，那样的话就早点说啦！」"

# game/S004.rpy:521
translate Chinese s004_77262231:

    "这几天我都那么烦恼着，到底算什么啊。"

# game/S004.rpy:522
translate Chinese s004_1162f439:

    "我不服气的呐喊声，在走廊中回响着。"

